1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 47-16 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to prohibited lease provisions in a contract to lease real property.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 47-16 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
5 and enacted as follows:
6 Fee for accepting check or other instrument of payment prohibited.
7 A landlord may not charge a tenant a fee to accept cash, a check, a money order, or similar
8 instrument for the payment of rent or any other payment required by the landlord under a lease
9 for real property.
